lanterne (0.4.0) unstable; urgency=low
  * Added check for camera cover status; Lanterne will now avoid turning LEDs on if cover is closed.  This check can be disabled from the new Preferences form (available from the drop-down menu).
  * Added ability to transmit Morse code text in a continuous loop.
  * Added option to run torch in a continuous pulse.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Thu, 30 May 2013 19:57:31 -0400

lanterne (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=low
  * Added ability to load text files for use in the morse code flasher.
  * Added a warning message about the brightness of the flash LEDs.  (Try not to look directly at them!)
  * Added ability to pause a running morse code transmission.
  * Added fix for rotation bug.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Wed, 29 May 2013 19:10:45 -0400

lanterne (0.2.0) unstable; urgency=low
  * Added new "Continuous SOS beacon" function.
  * Replaced "Torch" window with a simple on/off button.
  * Modified UI buttons to be more finger-friendly.
  * Added QSettings support for persistent storage of user parameters.
  * Modified Strobe timer to strobe first, not pause first.
  * Various improvements to package meta-data.

 -- John Pietrzak <jpietrzak8@gmail.com>  Tue, 28 May 2013 18:46:40 -0400

